FROM "Cases" 
WHERE "countyID" = $numberboxes)::decimal 
/
(SELECT sum("cases") AS "Gesamtsumme der Infektionen" 
FROM "Cases" 
WHERE "date" < now()-interval'1 week' 
AND "countyID" = $numberboxes)::decimal ) AS "R-Wert" 
FROM "Counties" 
INNER JOIN "Cases" ON "Counties"."id" = "Cases"."countyID"  
WHERE "countyID" = $numberboxes
